%% Intelligence Budget and ROI decision loop
flowchart TD
  A[PSM: scope, impact ceiling, budget remaining] --> B[Eligible capabilities from playbook + gates]
  B --> C[For each C: estimate cost and EQG]
  C --> D{ROI = EQG / cost}
  D -->|best ROI below threshold| E[stop_reason: roi / DR / budget]
  D -->|best ROI OK and affordable| F[Suggest C + benefit claim + skip condition]
  E --> G[Host reasons or implements with existing evidence]
  F --> H[Host optionally calls MCP tool]
  H --> I[Debit budget / update polish_loops / apply_envelope]
  I --> A
  G --> A
